high_descs: Move left to face the stove top
Pick up the tea kettle on the front right stove burner
Carry the kettle to the sink to the left of the trash an
Turn on the sink, wash then turn off the sink then pick it up
Carry the tea kettle back to the front right burner
Place the tea kettle on the front right burner
anns.task_desc: Move a tea kettle to the stove top

high_descs: Go to the left and face the stove.
Pick up the tea pot on the bottom right of the stove.
Turn around and stand in front of the sink.
Put the tea pot in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the tea pot back up.
Go left and cross the room to face the stove.
Put the tea pot on the bottom right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tea pot on the stove.

high_descs: Move over left to the front of the stove.
Pick up the tea kettle on the right front burner.
Turn around and go to the front of the sink on the left.
Wash the tea kettle with running water inside the sink and then pick it up.
Turn around to go back to the stove.
Place the tea kettle on the right front burner.
anns.task_desc: Wash the tea kettle and put it back.
